Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! What a huge town!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place used to be full of pirates\Non their way to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has everything you could ever need!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'm gonna go get equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for our upcoming great adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I can get\Nsome good ingredients here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good women, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got something I wanna buy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? How are you gonna do that?\NYou're flat broke, as I recall!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'm gonna check\Nout the execution platform!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna see where the King\Nof the Pirates was executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! We still haven't\Ndecided where to meet up at!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Pirates was\Nborn here and died here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might've even walked\Ndown this very street!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Town of the Beginning and End;\NLandfall at Loguetown"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How's this?\N--Oh! You look wonderful, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How's this?\N--You look so elegant, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.57,0:02:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How's this?\N--Elemental, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How's this?\N--Electrical!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How's this?\N--Elegy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be purchasing all of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't want 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want something that's rougher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! A top-quality aperitif!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Two Poinderine\Nchampagne-like beauties!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole town is brimming with\Nthe finest ingredients around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I can't decide\Nwhat to go after first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just found the main dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:22.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Love-Love Pirates"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! What is this place?!\NEverything here is a collector's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything here once belonged to pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who returned alive from the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are especially valuable goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then these are all items that went\Non adventures in the Grand Line?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absolutely correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only do business\Nwith warriors of the sea here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we warmly welcome\Ngentlemen such as yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say? This was the\Nfavorite gun of the Gold Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:04:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Gold Roger's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Show me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker! Terrible news!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A message from Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've received word that a\NMonkey D. Luffy and his pirate crew
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are headed here, to Loguetown!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just earned a 30 million\NBerry bounty in the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 million...\NThat's worthy of congratulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an incredibly evil villain
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who even defeated Don Krieg\Nand Arlong the fishman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn your shouting.\NYou made it fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:05:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good to be tense.\NI got my own pace I do things at.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... What, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! A pirate group!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Word has it they may\Nshow up in town today, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you so flustered for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have any pirates who've set\Nfoot into this town ever escaped
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since I took charge here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then calm the hell down.\NYou're gonna screw up my pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting, sir! We have word that\Npirates have appeared at the port!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go there at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Luffy's group!\NThey've definitely set foot into town!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 million, huh? I pray he\Nputs up at least a bit of a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just talking to myself. Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to look at this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:56.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Please give\Neach unit their orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:05:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you need to\Nconsider how powerful he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that. Where's Tashigi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. She mentioned she\Nwould be gone this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that she'd show up for training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That dumb girl.\NWhere the hell'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! A triple-scoop ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, now!\NYou'll drop them if you run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My ice cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm very sorry about my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!\NI'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout that.\NMy pants ate your ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, buy yourself five scoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's go.\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loot everything there is!\NDon't leave a single potato behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Gally the Crescent-sama,\Nwill use these vital food supplies
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on my way to becoming\NKing of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand it all over thankfully!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's in charge here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Monkey D. Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll test you and see if you're\Nworthy of setting foot into my town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me your crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He's one of the toughest\Nguys from Navy Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This town used to be a hangout\Nfor pirates headed for the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:08:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But ever since he took over, every\Nsingle pirate who's come into town
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has wound up in the slammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His strength is extraordinary.\NHe's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They even say he has\NDevil Fruit powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Fruit powers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible, Captain! You captured\NLuffy's crew in no time flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your eyes just for decoration?\NThis guy obviously isn't Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world'd be ending if this\Nshabby fly were worth 30 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then, where is Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll show up soon enough.\NThe fun is just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did I wind up at the port? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he one of these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing! Do you know how\Nto get to the execution platform?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The execution platform?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lost on my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen you around before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I just landed on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This town sure is huge!\NIt's way different from Fusha Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking for\Nthe execution platform?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see the place where\Nthe King of the Pirates died!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know where? Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Follow the smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That way?! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, these are expensive!\NToo expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend you money? Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But including interest, you'll hafta\Npay me 300% of what you borrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to borrow\Nany more from that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't go into the Grand Line\Nstuck with just one sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What do I do?\N-- "Monster"?! How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, shut up! Our boss is\Nbehind bars all thanks to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you still not learned your lesson?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! We ain't happy\Nwith things as they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna bring\Nyour corpse to him to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I will fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You will, girlie?!\N--Don't make us laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can a girl possibly do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Die!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--She did it!\N--You're strong, lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I can't tell if she's strong or weak!\N--Glasses! Glasses! Glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Glasses...\N--Hey. Are these them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry to bother you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--My glasses!\N--I-I didn't mean to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were expensive! How could\Nyou do something so horrible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I didn't mean to--!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay me back for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to get to\Nthe execution platform,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now I'm somewhere else completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. I'll get\Nthere sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:12:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold... Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you work here, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It said "Gold Roger"\Non the sign outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that this place's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scram.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't a place for a runt like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we're closed\Nfor good as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It went under?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't go under!\NI'm shutting it down myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just curious about\Nthe name, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lost. I was wanting\Nto go the execution platform...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me how to get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that on your table?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! A skull?! It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what became of a guy\Nonce known as Killer Giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A villain who sent hundreds\Nof pirates to the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Gold Roger sent him to\Nhis grave with just one blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With truly lightning speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy was famous for the\Nabsurdly huge blade he used,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but their fight ended\Nin the blink of an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the wound he received!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was an infamous scoundrel himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With his dying breath, he muttered,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Roger... My hat's off to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May you have honor\Nas the Eternal Pirate..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So awesome! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eric Down,\Nthe man known as King...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Silver,\Nthe world's greatest gunman...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant Gowns Brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:14:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were all tough men\Nwho were as feared as demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for Gold Roger,\Nthey were as weak as infants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would ya like to hear more?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very few people these days\Nbelieve this story, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay! Just tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In those days...\Nno, even still, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he was the one and only man\Nwho didn't fear the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, the Grand Line\Nwas an unknown area,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from which not a single boat ever\Nreturned after being swallowed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a sea of evil that people\Nfeared and which few approached!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man. Give me more rum.\NThe whole bottle'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are drinking happily, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am. I'm just about to take\Na little stroll into the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm excited beyond belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You're going there?!\NInto that sea of evil?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is there something\Nwrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not exactly, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take my advice.\NForget about going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's ever come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. Give me more rum.\NA whole barrel'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After saying that,\Nhe drank the whole place dry,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then set sail all too\Ncasually the next morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard he had conquered\Nthe Grand Line a bit later,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was more happy\Nthan I was surprised--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was more excited than\NI should have been at my age!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, 22 years ago today,\NRoger died on the execution platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day, everyone\Nproud of their great strength
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has tossed their hat\Ninto the pirate ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It marked the beginning\Nof the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now look! The town's full of\Nnothing but cowards and scum now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men crazy enough to challenge that\Nsea of evil are all but gone now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why this bar is\Nclosing down for good today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the Grand Line, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger's so cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's how a pirate should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I set out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to the Grand Line,\Nget the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those're some mighty big words!\NAnd in this bar, of all places!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only said what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiddo! If there're still\Npatrons like you out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe I'll hold off on closing this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know if there are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!\NOf course you wouldn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been in such\Na good mood since then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you to a drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't drink alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Then have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a toast!\NTo the Eternal King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the Eternal King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's certainly a warm hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for a regular patron of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap! You're tryin'\Nto shut the place down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wrong of you to\Nhold a grudge against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only come here as a loyal customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the pirates' fault that\Nthey're all cowards these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a customer? How rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a drink of rum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no alcohol for you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so iron-hearted.\NToday's a special day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I remember that day clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How Roger looked at the very end...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Main Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Gold Roger walk through here, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a humid afternoon,\Njust like today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His hands were shackled as\Nhe was led down the main street
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,toward the town square,\Nwhere the execution platform stood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:19:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, he walked like\Na triumphant general.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger had attained everything\Nthe world has to offer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he was\Nwalking toward death,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was literally\Na king of great pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any last words?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this off for me.\NIt's itchy beyond belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I would run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know how\Nto make a guy feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's get\Nthis over with quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you hide\Nall the treasure you found?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it in the Grand Line?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.38,0:20:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it, didn't you?!\NThat legendary treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shut up, you!\N--That great treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:21:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't speak without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!\N--Execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it all began...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:22:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.26,0:22:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new wanted poster!\NPut it up somewhere noticeable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Smoker!\NSorry for the rudeness, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.07,0:22:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.01,0:22:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.45,0:22:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.42,0:22:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where the King\Nof the Pirates was executed...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.09,0:22:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place where the\Ngreatest pirate in history died...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place where it began...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.57,0:23:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! This is a town\Nfor meeting pretty women!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty women, indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.71,0:24:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't relax! The marines\Nhere are supposedly tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.05,0:24:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?\NDid you buy your swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the problem. In any case,\NI gotta get me two more swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.99,0:24:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.42,0:24:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kitetsu III and Yubashiri! Zoro's New\NSwords and the Woman Sergeant Major"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
